title: Seahawks vs. Patriots: 1H Moneyline
market_description:
In the first half of the NFL game between Seahawks and Patriots, scheduled for February 8 at 6:30 PM ET:

This market will resolve to "Seahawks" if the Seahawks are winning at halftime.

This market will resolve to "Patriots" if the Patriots are winning at halftime.

If the score is tied at halftime, this market will resolve 50-50.

The result will be determined based on the score at halftime only.

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed. If the game is canceled entirely, with no make-up game, this market will resolve 50-50.

This market will resolve to "Hornets" if the Hornets win the game by 3 or more points.

If the game is postponed, this market will remain open until the game has been completed. If the game is canceled entirely, with no make-up game, this market will resolve 50-50.
